nodes.text: Wick 111 was a planet located in Outer Rim Territories region, that was the homeworld of the Wickwar Wazellman. The historian Eloc Throno included a map with the location of Wick 111 in his book Traveler's Guide to Batuu.
Wick 111 was first mentioned in Star Wars: Datapad, the mobile app companion to the Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge theme park land.
